The paper deals with designing neural architectures and model compression for deep learning applications, which are topics commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). However, since the paper focuses on designing neural architectures and quantization policies for mobile devices, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely categories.
